OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772193823
OL,3,CDudley Council to ditch injunction
OL,4,Cbanning street racing
OL,6,FDudley Council has applied to
OL,7,Fdiscontinue a High Court injunction
OL,8,Fbanning street racing in the borough,
OL,9,FITV News Central can reveal.
OL,11,FAt a hearing today, lawyers for the
OL,12,Fauthority confirmed it is "seeking to
OL,13,Fdiscontinue the claim" to continue the
OL,14,Fwide-ranging order.
OL,16,FThe court heard Dudley believes it has
OL,17,F"other means" of dealing with the
OL,18,Fproblem and no longer requires the
OL,19,Fprotection of the High Court order.
OL,26,@tD@[OUuD@VO]yD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
