OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772193823
OL,3,CDudley Council to ditch injunction
OL,4,Cbanning street racing
OL,6,FThe authority has put a Public Spaces
OL,7,FProtection Order in place instead,
OL,8,Fwhich it says will allow it to control
OL,9,Fcar cruising within its borough.
OL,11,FThe court heard that until Friday of
OL,12,Flast week, the council had been in
OL,13,Fdiscussions with the other local
OL,14,Fauthorities about its position, but it
OL,15,Fhas now decided it no longer wishes to
OL,16,Fpursue the injunction.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
