CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772193823
OL,3,CDudley Council to ditch injunction
OL,4,Cbanning street racing
OL,6,FThe injunction, first granted on 27
OL,7,FFebruary 2024, outlawed so-called "car
OL,8,Fcruising" or street racing across
OL,9,FWolverhampton, Dudley, Sandwell and
OL,10,FWalsall.
OL,12,FIt prohibits "anyone who is a driver,
OL,13,Frider or passenger in or on a motor
OL,14,Fvehicle from taking part between 3pm
OL,15,Fand 7am in a gathering of two or more
OL,16,Fpeople where motor racing, stunts or
OL,17,Fother dangerous or obstructive driving
OL,18,Ftakes place."
OL,26,@oD@cOUpD@IO]tD@NOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772193823
OL,3,CDudley Council to ditch injunction
OL,4,Cbanning street racing
OL,6,FIt also covers organisers and
OL,7,Fspectators, banning people from
OL,8,Fpromoting, organising or publicising
OL,9,Fthe gatherings.
OL,11,FPolice officers also have the power of
OL,12,Farrest if they believe the order is
OL,13,Fbreached and punishments include
OL,14,Fimprisonment, a fine or seizure of
OL,15,Fassets.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
