CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772193823
OL,3,CDudley Council to ditch injunction
OL,4,Cbanning street racing
OL,6,FThe other three Black Country
OL,7,Fauthorities - City of Wolverhampton
OL,8,FCouncil, Walsall Council and Sandwell
OL,9,FCouncil - all intend to press ahead
OL,10,Fwith maintaining the injunction and
OL,11,Fsay they continue to value it.
OL,13,FBirmingham City Council is also
OL,14,Fcovered by a similar injunction, which
OL,15,Fthe authority is appealing to have
OL,16,Fextended.
OL,18,FThe hearing was told that if that
OL,19,Fhappens, signs advertising the
OL,20,Finjunction around Dudley would have to
OL,21,Fbe removed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
