PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772193823
OL,3,CDudley Council to ditch injunction
OL,4,Cbanning street racing
OL,6,FSigns elsewhere in the Black Country
OL,7,Fwould need Dudley's logo to be
OL,8,F"removed, obscured or defaced", the
OL,9,Fcourt heard.
OL,11,FThe injunction currently runs until 27
OL,12,FFebruary 2027 and is subject to annual
OL,13,Freview.
OL,15,FThe application was originally led by
OL,16,FCity of Wolverhampton Council on
OL,17,Fbehalf of Dudley, Sandwell and Walsall
OL,18,Fcouncils, with support from West
OL,19,FMidlands Police.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
