OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772193823
OL,3,CDudley Council to ditch injunction
OL,4,Cbanning street racing
OL,6,FAt the last annual review hearing on
OL,7,F26 February 2025, The Honourable Mr
OL,8,FJustice Ritchie permitted the
OL,9,Finjunction to continue, with minor
OL,10,Famendments, after hearing evidence
OL,11,Fthere was a "pressing need" for it to
OL,12,Fremain in force.
OL,14,FToday the judge blamed Dudley Council
OL,15,Ffor a late change in its position
OL,16,Fsaying it: "Should have got its act
OL,17,Ftogether much earlier" as the date for
OL,18,Fthis review hearing had been in the
OL,19,Fdiary for a year.
OL,26,@sD@MOUsD@[O]xD@LOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772193823
OL,3,CDudley Council to ditch injunction
OL,4,Cbanning street racing
OL,6,FIn order to ditch the order, Dudley
OL,7,Fmust obtain permission from the court.
OL,9,FCouncillor Damian Corfield, cabinet
OL,10,Fmember for neighbourhoods at Dudley
OL,11,Fcouncil, said: "We continue to work
OL,12,Fclosely with neighbouring authorities
OL,13,Fand Police to tackle the issue of car
OL,14,Fcruising.
OL,16,F"However, following the implementation
OL,17,Fof a Public Space Protection Order
OL,18,F(PSPO) in Dudley borough, Dudley
OL,19,FCouncil has taken the decision to not
OL,20,Fto remain in the Black Country Car
OL,21,FCruising injunction.
OL,26,@sD@POUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772193823
OL,3,CDudley Council to ditch injunction
OL,4,Cbanning street racing
OL,6,F"The PSPO will continue to give us
OL,7,Fpowers to tackle reckless and
OL,8,Fdangerous driving on our roads, but
OL,9,Fthis move also means we can act
OL,10,Fagainst other dangerous antisocial
OL,11,Fbehaviour such as the offroad use of
OL,12,Fquadbikes and motorbikes.
OL,14,F"The issue of car cruising will remain
OL,15,Funder review and the council will
OL,16,Fcontinue to take appropriate steps to
OL,17,Fprotect the residents of this Borough
OL,18,Fand further curb this issue."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/9
